sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Link } from 'react-router-dom' export const DynamicListItem = ({ mappedItem, deleteItem }) => { return ( {mappedItem.name} {new Date(mappedItem.createdAt).toLocaleDateString()} at {new Date(mappedItem.createdAt).toLocaleTimeString()} {new Date (mappedItem.updatedAt).toLocaleTimeString()} {deleteItem(mappedItem._id)}}>Delete ) }
